(title मण्डूकानां सूर्योपालम्भः (rb The Frogs' Complaint against the Sun))
(author Aesop. Retelling & Translation: Dhiraj Eadara, Karthik Iyer)
(copyright © 2025. Dhiraj Eadara, Karthik Iyer. CC BY-SA)
